There were only a total
of 23 in the state.

00:27:30.070 --> 00:27:31.950
So you had a high
barrier to entry

00:27:31.950 --> 00:27:34.090
because of a regulatory issue.

00:27:34.090 --> 00:27:38.570
And what was interesting
in this 10-Q was,

00:27:38.570 --> 00:27:42.950
the fifth off-track betting
location that they built

