I'm saying, that's not a
bad business, you know?

00:27:59.630 --> 00:28:02.210
I took it upon myself
to go meet the CEO.

00:28:02.210 --> 00:28:04.550
We talked about the
importance of people.

00:28:04.550 --> 00:28:08.280
He was a real estate
developer by background.

00:28:08.280 --> 00:28:12.800
His father had control of this
old race track, Penn National

00:28:12.800 --> 00:28:15.830
Gaming, that had-- because
in Pennsylvania, they'd

00:28:15.830 --> 00:28:18.230
given the licenses for
the off-track betting

00:28:18.230 --> 00:28:22.250
to the legalized gambling
arena, the racetrack, the horse

00:28:22.250 --> 00:28:26.130
racetrack business,
